file.name: issue_10866_bigdecimal_default.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Demo
paths:
  '/test':
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Apa"
        required: true
      responses:
        200:
          description: Successful operation

components:
  schemas:
    Apa:
      type: object
      required:
        - bepa
        - cepa
      properties:
        bepa:
          type: number
          format: long
          default: 0
        cepa:
          type: number
          default: 6.28318
        depa:
          type: number
          default: 71
        epa:
          type: number
          nullable: false
          default: -71
        fepa:
          type: number
          nullable: true
          deprecated: true
          default: 100
        gepa:
          type: number
          nullable: true
